 He walked into the ship and heard Kluster's reply. He quickly headed towards 
the bridge. He reached it rather quickly.
"I have much to tell you. Prime as been turned evil. His brother Ultra Magus 
tried to revive him but failed inturn turning him into Gog Magnus. I am 
trusted with the chore of finding Prime and ridding his evil. I need your 
help."
